        "## QUESTION 2\n",
        "\n",
        "__Use the same query as above, but only include players with at least 10 at bats that year. Print the top 5 results.__  \n",
        "\n",
        "We can use the same logic as the before table with this query, only this time we filter out those who have been up to bat less than ten times, This decreases our averages shown in the top five because they had more chances at bat. "
      ],
      "id": "e051ab3f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Include and execute your code here\n",
        "\n",
        "q = \"\"\"\n",
        "    SELECT playerID, yearID, H,  AB, CAST (H AS FLOAT) / AB AS batting\n",
